# Measurement

Use this protocol node to capture or review the raw measurement output.

## Inputs

Sample ID: {{var|sample_id: str, title = "Sample ID", description = "Identifier received from the preparation node."}}

## Measurement Output

Raw data: {{var|raw_data: json, title = "Raw measurement data", description = "Structured measurement payload used by the analysis node."}}

Instrument: {{var|instrument: str = "uv-vis-alpha", title = "Instrument"}}

Operator note: {{var|measurement_note: AiralogyMarkdown, title = "Measurement note"}}

## Procedure

{{step|capture_measurement, check=True}} Capture the measurement and attach or paste the raw data payload.

{{check|measurement_ready}} Confirm that the raw data is ready for analysis.
